promptPrefix: Please create a social media post schedule for topics such as [PROMPT]  in the form of a table, where I am posting to Facebook, Instagram, Twitter, Pinterest, Tik Tok, and YouTube. The type of posts include; tips, tricks, quotes, facts, statistics, activity ideas, inspiration, lesson plan ideas, recipes, and lists. The format of these posts can be text, images, short videos or long format videos.[TARGETLANGUAGE]
title: Social Media Schedule
